Insider Activity


Individual




Steven B. Bing



Mr. Steven B. Bing is Independent Director at Almost Family, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Almost Family, Inc.
Mr. Bing was previously employed as Executive Director by The Kentucky Health Departments Association, Executive Director by The Kentucky Public Health Association, Inc., and Senior Vice President-New Business Development by National Rural Telecommunications Cooperative.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Kentucky and a graduate degree from the University of Louisville.



